{"tid":1641692,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【行動 】我要召集100個新人開twitter","createTime":"2019-10-09T12:09:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T18:42:29.000Z","uid":282414,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3eff92f4a800eabac54469ca522ee7f5efe969cb","tid":1641692,"uid":282414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:09:40.000Z","msg":"我知道香港人唔係玩開twitter，但唔該大家搞清楚，<br />\n好撚多識英文的大陸人／紅底人都玩twitter，佢地係大量大量分享撐警愛國建制言論<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我地要食住個風向分撲</span>：NBA事件／Blitzchung 事件／Tiffany &amp; Co. 事件都有好多外國人講，我地要製造輿論。<br />\n<br />\n我懇求大家：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 開個twitter account<br />\n2. 每日定時開post，分享圖片／外媒新聞／youtube片<br />\n3. 最最最重要，要反撲，主動去留言：</span><br />\n<br />\nA. <ins>如果有<span style=\"color: green;\">外國人</span>因為香港事件留言</ins>，<span style=\"color: green;\">入去講兩句，你可以多謝，你可以講下香港情況，務求趁對方有興趣就推送多少少資料</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nB. <ins>如果有<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍絲</span>因為香港事件留言</ins>，入去講兩句，<span style=\"color: blue;\">你可以睇下佢邏輯有咩問題，反駁下，務求等對方出醜，唔使改變佢地立場（impossible），總之要打破一言堂。</span><br />\n<br />\ntg：twitter特工小隊（無人我自刪）"},{"pid":"425d72c92e69d42f866885b346748c0cc4e097cf","tid":1641692,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:36:03.000Z","msg":"另類連儂牆 家家戶戶都知道<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1641528\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1641528</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b40fc0ceef18d75610a065a986c02327e64cb7c1","tid":1641692,"uid":148467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:41:48.000Z","msg":"唔識入你個tg grp 有無TG入grp教學"},{"pid":"b4e6b6df8740dffa56d6e04b0eb9ef26ab68e5c3","tid":1641692,"uid":148467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:43:42.000Z","msg":"定樓主已經del左grp?..."},{"pid":"50cd47ec688a234c0bae25d6d01a4b3f2cd2d0b0","tid":1641692,"uid":282414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4e6b6df8740dffa56d6e04b0eb9ef26ab68e5c3","tid":1641692,"uid":148467,"like":0,"dislike":0